      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f17b3138-e33f-11e1-9f91-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
